08" as="geometry"/></mxCell></object><object label="Suffering-focused&lt;br&gt;ethics&lt;br&gt;[1+2+3+4+5+6]&lt;br&gt;→ Shrimp Welfare Project&lt;br&gt;(Brian Tomasik, David Pearce)" tooltip="&lt;b&gt;parochial + far_away_humans + animals_somewhat + future_humans_matter_with_discounting + no_discounting_future_humans + animals_matter_a_lot + suffering_focused&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Asymmetry: averting intense suffering takes priority over creating happiness. Factory farming, malaria and the worst wild-animal conditions weigh up; speculative future-flourishing bets weigh down. Arises most naturally from taking animal suffering seriously, so it requires animals_somewhat. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 4 no_discounting_future_humans → 5 animals_matter_a_lot → 6 suffering_focused" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJzFWWtz08gS%2FStdKahrZyNbch6QUPmQhwMpAptNssveSygzlsb2rCWNmBlFMWz47ffMSPIjiYPZ%2B%2BFSRSEkTffp7tMv%2BdtaxAcsj82RjPja3lq7Tfv7%2B3SlmEjJSAoV%2BzrBRZHSdd7xgy0qpIqjG8ELKoJep7fZ2%2Bpt93aooY3MaKdpj1%2BnEHOgdZ5kRsiUwhGk7ZFPGVMyHAkWW2HBbocCGjDVYwWb9EZ5wlJdP%2BgQS0XCYt3TMuHFiJn6ySYNcpMrXh3oJcwYrnqFMKNeJHQo89SIdFi%2FvkWpnL%2FfWzhdv7U9VVeJY71YTlXukM4HA67ccRnmmkfOxC4LR8RmdgpNjM4nZoTrgYg5wYezx7pNxtrBokhvkOJwvEi5JqmcMMU9uIclHOqFxn0z4qXn%2FqVhcho6Ga8olEkmtbVw%2BgLOphGHRNwS2knThqURi2XKKUFk4xZ9ngaue%2FPZQrXH%2BW3GQ4ODNyzOOcmBkzCLccsJO%2BTaUD%2BfUG7V2IOazxu2R5cjJZKMPvAY8eR0ruRfkFueft193704uOoeU39CQ55yxQxvZZOaUDwSZsFN63i4gbCZEoz1JCQ5Wb%2BnIVfGmpxIBRpNPabLd0t3sCyLBdctupwkrVgOU6kQ28a3bHuDst3tu6aT5aK16z%2Bno9NX7s0%2BN6y8mynZZ30RCwMgfWnNjmw2fPQ3KPjUohMWGgmdsLUUhRcyG4PUbJCWxC0xpBoict2PxfHB2b%2Fbzz5Rn8eyAOHtWRdhfovreILjkA2vOlnQHeWhKWOB6HHQFOYPYpnj1AiBP67YTPsPDUSWtfyXzkx7%2BfKuSeTIBZmwoeBiOIJs5KTizOXJCN6yPNTUuJIJ02L8iv6AQfZZx%2B%2F4cNaU%2FedKALqZPK45aAWV4p3WdqWY3xrF5tSyG8TPiobNPAWNprKXqy8zds7qwInOcNMzIuH0C4XMMG2UzOAxm8BpzlxG2kRkyislVCRvXLBE80n7ErRJ6bv%2FvD1RdKPpvVTRiOWavgetbXvzFRTtg4