on — which rests on the sheer number of extra future lives saved from extinction — loses almost all its force. Only the harm to people who exist regardless still counts. This is the standard premise longtermism&#x27;s critics deny (discussed as the key objection in Greaves &amp; MacAskill&#x27;s &#x27;The Case for Strong Longtermism&#x27;). It requires no_discounting_future_humans, the astronomical-stakes move it pushes back on. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 4 no_discounting_future_humans → 5 animals_matter_a_lot → 6 suffering_focused → 9 living_in_simulation → 10 person_affecting_view" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJzFWe9z07gW%2FVc0HZiXlDqxk5bSMv3QHykwFLbbdmHfo0xQbCXWxraMJNc1bPnb35FsJ06blPA%2B7GOGwdjW1blX5x4dOd83AjamWaSPRcA29je6XXJwcECuJOUJ0YL4kn4rcJEn5Drrud42yYWMghvOcpJ7w96wP9we7gyfD%2FeGnktaSouUeG7bBLlOEOxQqSxONRcJ8UPE3CcuSakUfshpZEJ6ez3ikTGVQ5rTYhhmMU1U%2FaBHaMJjGqmhEjHLQ6rrJ30yznQmWTVgGFOtmRzmXIfDgCtfZInmyaR%2BfZskonl%2FuDC6fmtnNl0Vjg4jMZvyOVHZeMykHS78TLGgfrRHIn5j7vNkqHicRdRmXKeHlJlUIhlSjPft%2FKaAtkAD6oeEzqvEFaHkvNAhrsc8YgTrMH%2BsukSbKtAgUFtEMiweT5giQtpgkjkoLo0ZwHOF%2BzpkZd3%2FpVCwxLcxXhJfxKlQpj6zFzA2CRgi4hZXNprSNAloJBJGYrAj6pAvs8Uf3HwxUM1wdpsiKQy8oVHGiBjbCHOedGywI6Y0GWUFycw0ZqBizcT2yWUoeZySjywCGxg5l%2BIvxC1Hvxq8H1wcXg1OyKggE5YwSTXrpEVNShZwvVCmTTzcwqLrEoypJCLZWH8kPpPapBwLCRLOKqbKd8ty0DSNOFMdclnEnUhMEiHBjNb3dGeLpHs7d20by67WnvuUHL95ad8cMU3Lu6kUIzriEdcAMhIm7cB01Cd3i3ifO%2BSU%2BlpgTuRahsILqVmDRG8RJQgzxBBygpUbfMpPDs%2F%2B3X3ymYxYJHK0ixlrV5jd4joqMByxUVUbC3MHma%2FLtcDqMZAc6Y8jkWFUiIU%2FqXqBHDxMED3acV%2FYNM3li7s2IZZciIkccsYnIWKjoyWjtstCVMvwUJHWlYip4tOX5AMSMs96bs9FsWa9cy45oOti%2Bcxex6smft7ZqSZmt1rSxrT0ButnQiNnloBGs9irpy%2F7vZG1Z0OnuOloHjPyjPhUU6WlSFEx0%2F5JVnaxaUQqnTJCRfLWBY0VK7qXoE1CfrhPu4UkN4q8FzIIaabID6%2BzY26%2BxEQH4CGpxceUYqYQx8KoUYZlPJixp4UC7JWJn7caYiIzCBWacUJYIrJJSMbCtpEBV4lhu26HI2ESiZG8279OUoleS%2FQ5E2nETiW1KrC8%2FH3muLuzlXcxvFoDFZqeBJ9s8VngNKtV1oT6vsyspgjonZm