ometry x="486" y="956" width="251" height="108" as="geometry"/></mxCell></object><object label="Count soil animals&lt;br&gt;(~10^19 nematodes)&lt;br&gt;[1+2+3+4+5+6+10+11]&lt;br&gt;→ Shrimp Welfare Project&lt;br&gt;(Vasco Grilo)" tooltip="&lt;b&gt;parochial + far_away_humans + animals_somewhat + future_humans_matter_with_discounting + no_discounting_future_humans + animals_matter_a_lot + suffering_focused + person_affecting_view + soil_animals&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Grilo&#x27;s soil-animal accounting: ~10^19 soil nematodes, mites and springtails dominate the welfare effects of almost anything. Global-health charities raise food demand and cropland (~137 m^2-yr/$ for GiveWell top charities, ~1.11 kQALY/$ of soil-animal welfare change); with soil lives net-negative, the arithmetic makes GiveWell&#x27;s top charities net-harmful. Only enters once invertebrates already count, so it requires animals_matter_a_lot. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 4 no_discounting_future_humans → 5 animals_matter_a_lot → 6 suffering_focused → 10 person_affecting_view → 11 soil_animals" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJzFWf1v2zgS%2FVcGQYuz08iW7Hw0KfJDPpy2aNrNJdnt3jWFS0u0zbUkqqQUxe2mf%2Fs9UpItJ3aS3t7iChRVJXL4Zjjz5pH%2BvhbwIcvC9EgGfG1vrd2m%2Ff19ulRMxJRK8hX7NsVDHtNV1nG9TcqlCoNrwXPKvX6n3%2B1v9rf6233P7XseNXQqE%2FK8prFyFcPagdZZlKRCxuSPYXSPXEqYkv5YsNDY9HY75NGQqT7L2bQ%2FziIW6%2BpDh1gsIhbqvpYRz8csrb50aZilmeLlhH7E0pSrfi7ScT8Q2pdZnIp4VA3fpFjW3%2FcXZlejtmbLleZYP5SzJbdJZ8MhV3a69DPNg5kDcIorLeM%2BwwjfrmBjVH33SEsR9kvzNjI95o%2BJzcMjNDE6m6ZjPA9FyAk7MP%2Bs25Qa91kQ6A1SHNsmYq5JKmtMcQdRZREHaqHxPh3zIuD%2F0IhU7Fsbr8iXUSK1CcxsAObGAYdFvBIFNJ2yOGChjDlFyIuwRV9m2967%2FmKgmun8JoGvmHjNwoyTHFoL8wxpWWOHXKc0yKaUmWXMRM3rju3RxViJKKGPPEQacDpT8g%2FYLWa%2F7n3onR9c9o5pMKURj7liKW8l0yodeSDShTCt4%2BMGdjstwJhIwpK19Wvsc5UalyOpkH2ziOlibBEOliSh4LpFF9OoFcpRLBX2rPE92dqgZHfrtmlt2d3adZ%2FT0dtXduSAp6x4myg5YAMRihRABtK4HZha%2BuRukPe5RSfMTy