orce. Only the harm to people who exist regardless still counts. This is the standard premise longtermism&#x27;s critics deny (discussed as the key objection in Greaves &amp; MacAskill&#x27;s &#x27;The Case for Strong Longtermism&#x27;). It requires no_discounting_future_humans, the astronomical-stakes move it pushes back on. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 4 no_discounting_future_humans → 5 animals_matter_a_lot → 10 person_affecting_view" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJzFWG1z00gS%2FitTKaizQ2RLdrLZmMqHvDhAEdhckl32jlBmLI2tWUsaMTOKItjw2%2B%2BZkWTLjh3C3YejisJIPd1Pdz%2F9Mvq2FbAJzSJ9IgK2Ndjqdsnh4SG5lpQnRAviS%2Fq1wI88ITdZz%2FV2SS5kFNxylpPcG%2FVG%2FdHuaG%2FkuaSltEiJ57aNgpsEio6UyuJUc5EQP4S%2BAXFJSqXwQ04jo8476BGPTKgc0ZwWozCLaaLqFz1CEx7TSI2UiFkeUl2%2F6ZNJpjPJqgOjmGrN5CjnOhwFXPkiSzRPprX4LklE8%2Flo6XQttTc3V6mjo0jMTcK%2FlEklkhGdTJhv1ZgYWD%2BH1A8JXTjLFaHkotAhfk94xAhCuXitukQbZ2gQqB0iGeLPE6aIkFaZZA5iRGMGDFzhuQ5ZGb5%2FKPid%2BFbHS%2BKLOBXKuDkXwNkkYNCIR1xZbUrTJKCRSBiJkeCoQz7P8ze8%2FWygmuPsLoVTOHhLo4wRMbEaFqnuWGXHTGkyzgqSGTPmoGJNxwbkKpQ8TskHFiGpjFxI8Rf0lqdfDd8PL4%2Buh6dkXJApS5ikmnXSouYVC7heCtM2Xu4gd7oEYyIJTVbX74nPpDYux0KCS%2FOIqVK2DAdN04gz1SFXRdyJxDQREglufUv3dkh6sHfftrpstg7c5%2BTkzUsrOWaalk9TKcZ0zCOuAWQsjNuBKYqP7g7xPnXIGfW1gE34WqqCQGpykOgdogRhhhhCTpG54cf89Oj8X91nn8iYRSIH681Zm2F2h99RgePQjahaXbAdZL4uc4HsMXAV7pfcPa3YTA5RP8RI46GjeczIC%2BJTTZWWIsUxQ%2BUko5aWho1UOqWGKtOtSxorVnSvELuEfHefdwtJbhV5L2QQ0kyR715nzzx8CUOHSAapCwnBSyUIkOgLJtKInUlqqQmpB%2BEekD5z3H0bdTSBjuu6%2Ffu2Ba5CQxQ4SW%2BRURY4TfQlRur7MrNEFyhCY4vkIYJ7x0FHmhRoHQPyvc88j1SISMQnzCkYRW5AW2H0xUiCx7y9F4iJKYsZq7h0yiU4SpitaxOkRtZS0JnKAilLUKU%2Bx%2B8dcjw8%2B%2B1yWDLPasgZn4amJWxmWl1o83fGBVSPzoWjOGhlFZUsNLIfq5Of6uqgyJ9E1Tli4sR0mnCdBYwc%2F3Y9PAHVingsIu5bziGOhdVmKNNqV3QzfE5oVGhIofBCW79QqmiMgAadsomVXk%2F41DCkaiFTWRHfDAS4oEQmfXQcbvqF6XamvvEwfcu1H7KkpMNrFqUsuGDydxWspwRosDdnhC3GhhJ0kGjMENJXKORT4N6ow%2FUWtPJWtJwYojJpSi2j0TFNZn9YRpW6soRPoKvldqACEJbPGqN