gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Asymmetry: averting intense suffering takes priority over creating happiness. Factory farming, malaria and the worst wild-animal conditions weigh up; speculative future-flourishing bets weigh down. Arises most naturally from taking animal suffering seriously, so it requires animals_somewhat. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 4 no_discounting_future_humans → 6 suffering_focused" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJzFWWtT28gS%2FStdVFLXZpEtmVcgxQceJqFCsiywy94bUmQsje1ZSxplZoRwsuS33zMjyQ%2BwCdn74aZqax1ppvt0z%2BnuM8q3lYj3WR6bQxnxld2Vdpv29vboUjGRkpEUKvZ1jB9FStd5xw82qJAqjm4FL6gIbjo36zcbN1vU0EZmtNW0m69TGNnXOk8yI2RK4RC2dsmnjCkZDgWLralgp0MB9Zm6YQUb3wzzhKW6ftEhloqExfpGy4QXQ2bqN%2BvUz02ueLXhJmHGcHVTCDO8iYQOZZ4akQ7q5RuUytnnN3O761VbpPN%2Bnyu3QIa55pELosvCIbFpJEITo7OxGeJ3X8SckKPpa90mY5GyKNJrpDgSK1KuSSpnTHEPCWAJB16h8dwMeZmbf2kElYbOxmsKZZJJbWOYLMDeNOKwiEdCO2vasDRisUw5JTi5uEWfJwfTvf1sodrt%2FC7jocHGWxbnnGTfWZieYcsZO%2BDaUC8fU27d2I2azwa2S%2FsnpFmfmzE1znlUSBnRORYxFQ6bpY033Q%2Fd8%2F3L7hH1xjTgKVfM8FY2rmnDI2HmkrWKl2s4HlNCsvmEJWfr9zTkytjAE6lAl0nedLm2TArLslhw3aKLcdKK5SCVCpRpfMs21yjb2bxvOlvuzHb8l3R48tqt7HHDyqeZkj3WE7EwANKTNvjIcv6jv0bBpxYds9BI%2BGSKl6awILMnkZo10pK4pYdUA5xf92NxtH%2F67%2FaLT9TjsSxAbLvXnTO%2Fw%2B94jO2wjdw6W%2FAd5aEpTwRnyEFHhN%2BPZY5dQxz%2FUcVa2nscIKqp5b9yYdqfr%2B6bRI5isIkYCi4GQ9hG7SnOXD0MkS3LRk2NS5kwLUav6Q8EZN91%2FI6PZE1q4EwJQMdZL%2FQctILK8VZrs3LM74xiM27ZLc7PmkbMPAWZJraXuy8rcybqwJnO8NAzIuH0C4XMMG2UzJAxW%2Fdpzlxd2nJkyistVFRvnLNE83H7ArRJ6bv%2Fsj1WdKvpg1TRkOWavgetTfvwNRztgYdUt4lmxcIjoVA7xIE8dFHNnHem0J7UGIedospDgd9rdNA9%2FvW8W3LWWSgTghiXc7Qu1Mk7KoYSCTOF9LSIqkZU8teu%2FVjt%2FFTXFUP4ClXryb6XsEEqTB5xOvj1snsIko6TnoxF6NiKMxk7a5ZsjWZFVFsJKYvHBqtQskNX%2FzCqWZLFPGqVTbCMui8GNsFVCxqoqmTspEAIGtQN0bGE7Te2WxoQGg%2Bzd8KEQ56ecQmLb3mc8eiMq991tJTamxNquzKeMXLF47jHkdI3aAFHwL3Uhh9MjPjBAyuH9py5skWas%2FiApaM%2FHGlKW3kq%2BrDV8C3TAWF%2Br3U6gf90eKv0JPJVagTk0Y9xlZ1saEymd9vtoihaA3HLCxhs4WDatshU6kq