umans + living_in_simulation + person_affecting_view&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Person-affecting population ethics: making happy people is neutral, so the astronomical case for x-risk reduction — which rests on the sheer number of extra future lives saved from extinction — loses almost all its force. Only the harm to people who exist regardless still counts. This is the standard premise longtermism&#x27;s critics deny (discussed as the key objection in Greaves &amp; MacAskill&#x27;s &#x27;The Case for Strong Longtermism&#x27;). It requires no_discounting_future_humans, the astronomical-stakes move it pushes back on. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 4 no_discounting_future_humans → 9 living_in_simulation → 10 person_affecting_view" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJzFWG1z00gS%2FitdKaizQ2RLTrLZhMqHvDhAEdhckl32jlBmLI2tWUsaMSNFMWz47ffMSLJlxw7hw9ZRRWGkmX59uvtpfdsI%2BIjlUXYiA75xsNHt0uHhIV0rJhLKJPmKfZ3iR5HQTd5zvR0qpIqCW8ELKrxBb7A92BnsDzyXWjqTKXlu2wi4SSDoSOs8TjMhE%2FJDyDsgl1KmpB8KFhlx3n6PPBoxNWAFmw7CPGaJrl%2F0iCUiZpEeaBnzImRZ%2FWabRnmWK15dGMQsy7gaFCILB4HQvsyTTCTj%2BvgOJbL5fLBwuz61T5G4NW9FMtAiziNmDa%2BthOVcaZkM2GjEfSvGxMD62Wd%2BSGzurNDE6GKahfg9EhEnhHL%2BWncpM86wINBbpDjiLxKuSSorTHEHMWIxh0tC43kW8jJ8%2F9LwO%2FGtjJfkyziV2rg5O4C7ScAhEY%2BEttJ0xpKARTLhFCPBUYc%2Bz%2FLXv%2F1sTDXX%2BV0Kp3DxlkU5JzmyEuap7lhhx1xnNMynlBs15qLmTccO6BqyXpuwcjrnbJzz8uKr%2Fvv%2B5dF1%2F5SGUxrzhCuW8U46rSHFA5EtRGgTL7eQtqy0wwQRkqys3xOfq8x4G0sFGM2CpcuzZSRYmkaC6w5dTeNOJMeJVIBS61u6u0Xp%2Fu5928qyidp3n9PJm5f25JBnrHyaKjlkQxGJDIYMpfE4MPXw0d0i71OHzpifSehkipeicCA14U%2ByLdKSuMGEVGMkrf%2BxOD06%2F0%2F32Sca8kgWALy5a5PL7%2FA7muI6ZCOgVhZ0B7mflWlA4jhgCvdL2J5WQKZDlA6Z03joZCLm9IJ8ljGdKZnimimKJC9RbIDIlFNKqJLcumSx5tPuFWKX0Hf3eXeq6FbTe6mCkOWavnudXfPwJRQdIhlU1xCCN6%2BQE2mKKocvh7MQtrwt2m9b6y5ajWJSOeoNYBwTT2Q%2BDmkkLYyMcVVNt2tMHEvjSEw9192%2BSVIFrCXZBZdpxM8Us1VQaVxI7wFtc8fds1lGv%2Bm4uH5fmqJDJMsEld0CQTxwmtEqY8J8X%2BW2piTq3eiiIkQy7wSQz5IputQ